title: Fierce Fight for the Walls: Naval reinforcements - Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD Mod Gameplay
description:
Another glorious siege battle is underway.  This time the attackers are attacking by land and Sea.  By attacking the settlement in every direction they hope to destroy their enemies.  Enjoy the Siege battle :D

Attackers:
Empire of Nicaea  
Kingdom of France
Republic of Venice

Defenders:
Duchy of Saxony
Kingdom of England
Kingdom of Jerusalem

Medieval Kingdoms Total War 1212AD is a Mod for Total War Attila 

If you enjoyed the video don't forget to Like and Leave a comment :D
